parameters: 00_st_akane02_anger
Akane: Sigh... Looks like we're camping out again tonight...

Reisha: We finally saw a town, but after buying food, we
barely have anything left, let alone enough for lodging...
00_st_akane02_anger

Akane: We managed to escape from the mining pit, but when
you think about it, we were thrown out with not a penny to
our names. It's quite something that we're even walking
around in decent clothes...

Reisha: The royal capital is still a long way off, so let's
use this place as a base for now and think of ways to make
money. Tomorrow, let's stop by the guild and look for some
adventurer work we can take on.
00_st_akane02_serious
Akane: (…)

Akane: If you take your sweet time with jobs like that, have
you thought about when we'll ever get to the royal capital?
We're in a hurry, aren't we?

Reisha: Even so... We're in a situation where we're worried
about tomorrow's meal, you know?
00_st_akane02_serious
Akane: (…)

Reisha: How about manual labor? I can handle it, but if it's
something Akane can do too... If we had a decent amount of
money, we could even hire a horse...
00_st_akane02_serious
Akane: (…)
Akane: First of all...
Reisha: Hm? What's wrong?
00_st_akane02_serious

Akane: Don't you have any questions about the way this
conversation is going? Not even a little?

Reisha: We escaped with nothing but the clothes on our backs
and parted ways with the other workers to head for the royal
capital. And now we're strapped for cash. That's just how it
is. What's the problem?
00_st_akane02_anger

Akane: Then why the hell are you so fully equipped?! That's
what I wanna scream at you!!

Reisha: This? This is a knight's pride. A knight must always
be virtuous and refined. That doesn't change even when
traveling.
00_st_akane02_anger

Akane: That's what I'm saying! The reason we're strapped for
cash now is because you spent most of the little money we
earned on that gear!!!
Reisha: Please don't raise your voice. It's a bit scary.
00_st_akane02_anger

Akane: Not only that, but whenever you see someone
struggling by the hearth, you go 'It's charity' and give
away even more of our scarce money! That's why our own
stomachs are empty!

Reisha: Generosity is a knightly virtue. Even if we have to
cut back a bit, we must maintain a demeanor of abundance. We
can just be frugal in other ways. You understand, right?
00_st_akane02_anger
Akane: I'm not a knight----!!!
00_st_akane02_anger

Akane: If we're short on money, why don't we just steal it?!
I'll pick out something that won't cause them trouble if
it's gone, and I'll sneakily take care of it!
Reisha: (Gritting teeth...!)
00_st_akane02_anger

Akane: Jo-, it was just a joke...! Don't glare at me like
that!! You're huge and it's scary!!

Reisha: Good to know. Next time, try to come up with a joke
that's actually funny, alright?
00_st_akane02_anger
Akane: Da-!! Mo-----!!!
00_st_akane02_anger

Akane: Can't swap my back for my belly. No choice then, I
guess I'll have to accept less of a share and get hired.
They must have costumes for rent or something!!!

Reisha: What's up, Akane? Going into town? Did you come up
with a good idea?
00_st_akane02_anger

Akane: Yeah, I've got one. There's a perfect plan for female
adventurers like us. Hey, Reisha. Do you have any experience
with massages?

Reisha: Massage, huh! I see, I do have some knowledge in
that area.

Reisha: I've done it during the brief moments between combat
and training with my subordinates. It's really good for
recovering from fatigue. Stretching out the muscles firmly
can relieve stiffness and clear the mind.

Reisha: Not just that. When invited as a guest to the court,
I've also received treatments as part of the hospitality.
They used rare oils and herbs then. That was exceptional
indeed, yes indeed.

Reisha: It's been a while since I've done it for someone
else, but I should be able to do it well. A masseuse, huh?
Yeah, that's not bad!
00_st_akane02_nomal

Akane: Huh? Really? That's unexpected but better if you're
used to it. Then let's go. And let's get a bath while we're
at it.
